#       Configuration file for 3D Ball Advection MHD problem

REQUIRES physics/Hydro/HydroMain
REQUIRES physics/Eos/EosMain/Gamma

D   tiny	    Threshold value used for numerical zero
D   rx	            Field loop advection angle = atan(rx/ry)
D   ry
D   xCtr	    x center of the computational domain
D   yCtr	    y center of the computational domain
D   zCtr	    z center of the computatoinal domain
D   Ux_initial	    Strength of initial vector fields
D   Uy_initial	    Strength of initial vector fields
D   Uz_initial	    Strength of initial vector fields
D   ballRadius	    Radius of field loop

PARAMETER tiny         REAL     1.e-16
PARAMETER rx	       REAL     1.
PARAMETER ry           REAL     2.
PARAMETER xCtr	       REAL     1.
PARAMETER yCtr	       REAL     0.5
PARAMETER zCtr	       REAL     0.0
PARAMETER Ux_initial    REAL    1.0
PARAMETER Uy_initial    REAL    1.0
PARAMETER Uz_initial    REAL    1.0
PARAMETER ballRadius  REAL     0.1
